<refsect1 role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
This private class is used to represent the grant database and provides read/write functions to access it.</para>
<para>

</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1 role="details">
<title role="details.title">Details</title>
<refsect2>
<title><anchor id="PolKitGrantDbGrantType" role="enum"/>enum PolKitGrantDbGrantType</title>
<indexterm><primary>PolKitGrantDbGrantType</primary></indexterm><programlisting>typedef enum {
        POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_PROCESS,
        POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_SESSION,
        POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_ALWAYS
} PolKitGrantDbGrantType;
</programlisting>
<para>
Defines the type and scope of a privilege grant.</para>
<para>

</para><variablelist role="enum">
<varlistentry>
<term><anchor id="POLKIT-GRANTDB-GRANT-TYPE-PROCESS:CAPS" role="constant"/><literal>POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_PROCESS</literal></term>
<listitem><simpara> The privilege was granted to a process
</simpara></listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry>
<term><anchor id="POLKIT-GRANTDB-GRANT-TYPE-SESSION:CAPS" role="constant"/><literal>POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_SESSION</literal></term>
<listitem><simpara> The privilege was granted to session
</simpara></listitem>
</varlistentry>
<varlistentry>
<term><anchor id="POLKIT-GRANTDB-GRANT-TYPE-ALWAYS:CAPS" role="constant"/><literal>POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_ALWAYS</literal></term>
<listitem><simpara> The privilege was granted permanently
</simpara></listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>
<refsect2>
<title><anchor id="PolKitGrantDbForeachFunc" role="function"/>PolKitGrantDbForeachFunc ()</title>
<indexterm><primary>PolKitGrantDbForeachFunc</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                (*PolKitGrantDbForeachFunc)         (const <link linkend="char">char</link> *action_id,
                                                         <link linkend="uid-t">uid_t</link> uid,
                                                         <link linkend="time-t">time_t</link> when,
                                                         <link linkend="PolKitGrantDbGrantType">PolKitGrantDbGrantType</link> grant_type,
                                                         <link linkend="pid-t">pid_t</link> pid,
                                                         <link linkend="polkit-uint64-t">polkit_uint64_t</link> pid_time,
                                                         const <link linkend="char">char</link> *session_id,
                                                         <link linkend="void">void</link> *user_data);</programlisting>
<para>
Callback function for <link linkend="polkit-policy-cache-foreach"><function>polkit_policy_cache_foreach()</function></link>.</para>
<para>

</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>action_id</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> Identifer for the action granted
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>uid</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the UNIX process id, or -1 if the passed grant_type is not POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_ALWAYS
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>when</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> when the privilege was granted
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>grant_type</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the type of grant; one of <link linkend="PolKitGrantDbGrantType"><type>PolKitGrantDbGrantType</type></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>pid</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the process id, or -1 if the passed grant_type is not POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_PROCESS
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>pid_time</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the start time of the process (only if pid is set)
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>session_id</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the session id, or NULL if the passed grant_type is not POLKIT_GRANTDB_GRANT_TYPE_SESSION
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>user_data</parameter>&nbsp;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> user data passed to <link linkend="polkit-grantdb-foreach"><function>polkit_grantdb_foreach()</function></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>

</refsect1>




</refentry>
